  <para>The <emphasis role="bold"><!-- DNT-Start -->Nodes<!-- DNT-End --> </emphasis>function returns the number
  of nodes in the Thor cluster (always returns 1 on hThor and Roxie). This
  number is the same as the <!-- DNT-Start -->CLUSTERSIZE<!-- DNT-End --> compile time constant. The <!-- DNT-Start -->Nodes<!-- DNT-End -->
  function is evaluated each time it is called, so the choice to use the
  function versus the constant depends upon the circumstances.</para>

  <para>Example:</para>

  <!-- DNT-Start --><programlisting format="linespecific">A := STD.System.Thorlib.Nodes();</programlisting><!-- DNT-End -->
